the accessible education center offers a poster series, "distinguished people with disabilities," as a special thank you for people who have made a contribution to our student scholarship fund. there are 14 posters in the series. currently, 12 of the 14 posters are available. the aec will send a set of posters for contributions to the scholarship fund starting at the $30 level. contribution levels: if you have not made a contribution but would like to, please mail a check or money order only made out to: sjsu tower foundation; disabled students scholarship fund. please mail your check request to: san jose state university accessible education center one washington square san jose, ca 95192-0168 allow two to three weeks for delivery of the posters upon receipt of your contribution. your contribution allows aec to annually award scholarships to students with disabilities. once again, thank you for your interest in our poster series.  office emails staff directory administration building (adm) room 110 accessible education center san jos√© state university one washington square san jose, ca 95192-0168 mon: 9 am - 5 pm tues: 9 am - 5 pm wed: 10 am - 5 pm thurs: 9 am - 4 pm fri: 9 am - 4 pm 